    <thetext>Content assist should propose keyword &apos;super&apos; in the places it appears in this snippet:

public class Main implements Intf {
    class Inner {
        {
            Main.super.hashCode();
        }
    }
    @Override
    public void foo() {
        Intf.super.foo();
    }
}

Implementation hint: Looks like keyword &apos;this&apos; is implemented here: org.eclipse.jdt.internal.codeassist.CompletionEngine.findMembers(char[], ReferenceBinding, Scope, InvocationSite, boolean, Binding[], int[], int[], boolean)</thetext>
